Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.60,0:00:41.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind. Open your mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:57.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Far beyond the deep blue Earth,\Nyou and I shall meet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.69,0:00:59.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as a gentle breeze goes by.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.05,0:01:03.06,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:04.53,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.53,0:01:11.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A snow-white feather comes fluttering\Ndown, swaying gently in the air.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.66,0:01:18.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without holding back, I want to\Nenvelope you, my one and only love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.77,0:01:28.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know I have the power to protect\Nthe one I love, right here in my hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.18,0:01:34.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind.\NJust as I've always dreamed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.92,0:01:41.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let the wind carry off\Nyour hopes, faraway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:48.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have wings nobody can see.\NLook, you have them, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.60,0:01:56.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They'll take us to where we can be free.\NAnyone can be free.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.91,0:02:01.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sky is so blue...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.69,0:02:12.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This infinite space is brimming\Nwith so many different forms of life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:16.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The source of life can\Nalso be found in this space...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:23.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as the cycle of birth repeats itself\Nwithin the endless flow of time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.57,0:02:30.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So how did this Great Space\Ncome into being?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.38,0:02:34.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These stars that are born,\Nonly to vanish...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:38.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In what way are\Ntheir destinies determined?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.82,0:02:45.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fate... are all living things\Nsteered by this thing called fate?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:52.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And on this tiny planet as well...\Nlife exists in many forms...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:56.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and there is much that is\Nleft in the hands of fate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.60,0:03:00.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Life begins and life ends, as well...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.64,0:03:06.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In this brief passage of time, people\Nlive out their lives in different ways...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:09.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...until at last their lives\Ncome to an end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:15.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And this species has always followed\Nits desires. It has continued to evolve...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:17.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thriving...\NDeclining...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:21.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Inventing...\NDestroying...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:29.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And is the human race, which has\Ncreated all this, also controlled by Fate?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:33.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this something that\Ncan ever be changed?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:40.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What if the control over one's fate was\Nwrested away by an Unknown Being...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:43.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...independently of one's will?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.02,0:03:48.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If indeed your fate is being controlled\Nby the hands of this Unknown Being...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:52.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...then who in the world\Ncan this Unknown be?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:03:59.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.07,0:04:04.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Morisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.94,0:04:07.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Time to get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:11.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:26.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Keiichi Morisato, a sophomore at\Nthe Nekomi Institute of Technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:29.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I'd put my lonely\Nhigh school days behind me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:33.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and I was ready to plunge into all\Nthe fun that college life had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:37.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But the Auto Club I joined is on a tight\Nbudget. We can't do any real activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:41.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, we spend all\Nour time working out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:43.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I moved into a dorm for the low rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:47.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Life is chaotic with colorful characters,\Nespecially the Auto Club president.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:50.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Also, for some reason, no women\Nare allowed in this dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:53.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't discovered the reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:57.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looks like it'll be another\Ngorgeous day this afternoon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:05:02.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's now time for your Daily Horoscope.\NLet's start with Taurus.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.09,0:05:07.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Today is the day to go after your\Ndreams with support from your friends.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:10.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gemini, you will gain popularity\Non the strength of your caring nature.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:14.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lend a helpful ear to\Nyour troubled younger friends.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:19.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Capricorn. Today is not your day,\Nno matter what you do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:22.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bummer...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:28.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's no use sweating\Nover your horoscope, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:32.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Back to sleep now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:48.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:50.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:05.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can't afford to flunk 2nd period\NGerman...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:13.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:20.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For him, this is\Na daily occurrence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:26.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is in this manner\Nthat his day unfolds.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:33.79,AMG episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah! You're a Goddess?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:36.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nekomi Institute of Technology{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:52.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, it happened back\Nin the spring of my freshman year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.71,0:06:57.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In order to bid farewell to the person\NI was, I made a life-changing decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.58,0:07:00.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to ask that girl out on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:08.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:13.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Mishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:17.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to go on\Na museum tour with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:23.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm not into\Nold-fogey stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:28.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe if you shot up another 7 or 8\Ninches, I'd be inclined to think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:29.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:38.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the mass ''m'' that\Nappears in this equation...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:40.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't ever want to remember...\N{\i1}Today's my day to pick on white shirts!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:42.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Today's my day to pick on white shirts!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.76,0:07:45.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about you, Morisato.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:49.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the day that I call on\Nwhoever's wearing a white shirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.33,0:07:51.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You see anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.23,0:07:54.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But you picked on white last time, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:57.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm wearing white, too.\NDo you have a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.21,0:07:59.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Answer the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.67,0:08:01.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:07.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped. That's it for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:12.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Saved by the bell! Maybe\NI have luck on my side today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.92,0:08:14.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:15.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Today's your lucky day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:17.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:22.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, why don't we go and show\Neveryone what we're made of?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.26,0:08:27.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You said it! We must go and make a\Nstrong push for more funding next year!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:32.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, actually, I have a\NGerman class right after this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:34.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:37.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all the loyalty\Nyou can muster for our club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:41.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know we didn't raise you\Nto be that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:41.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't raise me at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:42.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On November 15th of last year...{\i0}\NYou didn't raise me at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:44.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On November 15th of last year...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:47.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When you lost your wallet\Nand starved yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:50.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...we gave you our onions and cabbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:53.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you've forgotten that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.03,0:08:55.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We can discuss the\Ndetails in the clubhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:59.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I have a class to go to!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.47,0:09:07.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And above this young man's head,\Na star shone constantly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:10.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is called the Star of Misfortune.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:14.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It exerts a constant influence\Nover whomever it targets.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:19.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why did this star appear over\Nthe head of Keiichi Morisato?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:22.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What can we call it but Fate?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:24.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, as you can see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.19,0:09:28.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the Auto Club has run through\Nits budget for this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:30.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:33.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because Tamiya got busted\Nfor stealing the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:37.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...from the Assistant Dean's\Noffice and using it as a picture frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.24,0:09:39.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:42.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be no club activities\Nfor the rest of the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:45.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, today we will\Ndevote ourselves to fundraising!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.55,0:09:50.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, bring your repairs to us...\Nno job too small!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:52.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your bicycles, your cars...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:56.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your radio-controlled toys, your\Ntricycles, anything that has wheels...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:58.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can turn to us\Nwith all your problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.83,0:10:02.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Auto Club's big chance\Nto offer our services and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:04.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...hard-earned skills to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:06.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So embarrassing...{\i0}\N...hard-earned skills to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:10.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There goes the Auto Club,\Npulling another bizarre stunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:15.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And they wonder why they can't get\Nany girls to join!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:17.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There is that one girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:25.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Got car or motorcycle problems? Just\Nleave it to the Nekomi Tech Auto Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:29.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Auto Club!\NCan you guys check this out for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:35.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The engine doesn't start. I don't think\Nit's a problem with the spark plug...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:38.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, gotcha! No problemo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:39.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it, Dai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:42.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You got it, Den-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:45.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:50.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:56.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:11:00.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's all she wrote, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:04.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,An Auto Club original,\Nthe ''Tamiya Special''!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:08.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I never asked you\Nto customize the thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:13.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just take it for a spin and you'll\Nbe blown away by how spectacular it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:20.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's working!\NSo how much do I owe you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:22.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,30,000...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:27.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but since you're getting a discount\Ntoday, that'll be just 15,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.61,0:11:32.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! You think you're gonna\Ndrive off without paying for my service?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:34.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Go after him, Morisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:35.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.06,0:11:42.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You make him cough up that money!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:45.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding?\NI can't fork over 30,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.69,0:11:50.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know the seniors. If I don't bring back\Nthe money, there'll be hell to pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:53.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I better take a shortcut, or\Nhe'll make it off school grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:55.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.14,0:12:23.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:26.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your patronage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:31.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I'll escape the wrath\Nof the seniors now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:33.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Morisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:34.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:38.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with the Tea Ceremony Club. What\Nare you going to do about this vase?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:42.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with the Cooking Club. You messed\Nup five of our plates. We can't cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:47.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with the Sewing Club! You're going\Nto do something about this, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:50.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with the Fortune-telling Club...\Nnothing will go your way today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:11.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They even made me hand\Nover my lunch money...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:15.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too broke now to do anything today .
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:21.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right? Well, I guess\Nwe have no choice, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:26.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Man! This would have\Nto happen on a Saturday!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:30.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Since my bike's on the blink, I guess\Nthere's nothing to do but sit at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.14,0:13:35.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Pasta sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:37.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:42.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A girlfriend, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:47.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I got this bike just so\NI could take you for a ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:50.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! How lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:54.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go, and gaze upon\Nthe sunset at the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:02.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:05.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Since my horoscope was pretty lousy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:08.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I might as well go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:15.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nekomi Station{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:35.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you were late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:36.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:41.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you using my kotatsu\Nto warm up again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:45.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right, being that we have\Nsome business with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:49.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't think that\Nhas anything to do with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.75,0:14:52.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, we're\Nall going out tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:54.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:58.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's a party tonight that\Nwe absolutely can't miss, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:01.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's Saturday, I was planning\Nto go out, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:07.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your Beemer's out of commission, so\Nyou won't be going anywhere, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:11.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It just wouldn't do to leave\Nour precious dorm standing empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:14.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'll be fine if we just lock it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:16.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can you guarantee that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:18.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure nothing will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:22.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What if you lose your precious\Nboom box from Den-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:25.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How about your erotic magazine stash\Nin the closet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:28.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We all know we can trust in you,\NMorisato.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:29.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:34.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I figured it wouldn't be any fun,\Njust holding down the fort here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:38.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So here's a list of tasks for you...\Ndo them all and you won't be bored!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:41.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we're counting on you, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:49.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A list of today's tasks{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:52.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm gonna have to do it!\N{\i1}A list of today's tasks{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.23,0:16:15.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Home Delivery{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:46.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:51.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keiichi Morisato was born\Nto be taken advantage of.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:56.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now that it's come to this, we can't\Nvery well look the other way, can we?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:31.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now all I have to do is wait for\Nthat call for Aoyama.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.51,0:17:35.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He said it would be\Naround seven or so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:48.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's over, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:02.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Uh-oh, it's due today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.71,0:18:06.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any money for late fees!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:12.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just might make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.86,0:18:26.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's not my\Nlucky day today, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:52.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I can't just stand by\Nand do nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.46,0:18:55.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:57.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:19:02.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was sent to do the shopping\Nand I lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:07.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...my mother's wallet.\NI lost it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.17,0:19:10.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And now I can't buy the fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:14.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see, you dropped\Nyour wallet somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:15.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:19.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we look for it together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:21.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:24.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When did you realize\Nyou'd dropped the wallet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:29.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,After I bought the radishes,\NI went to buy the fish, and it was gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:33.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then let's go back\Nto the shopping arcade.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:43.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:45.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You dropped your wallet, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:47.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My wallet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:50.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Be more careful from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:54.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. But now I can buy the fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:58.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Good for you\Nto be running errands!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:20:02.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother! Now I can\Nbuy the fish... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:04.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.88,0:20:23.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.48,0:20:25.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:29.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama has gone to\Na college party tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:32.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be back at around 9 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:35.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I got that.\NI'll give him the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:37.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:42.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That was a close call.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:46.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd missed that call,\NI would've been in huge trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:57.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I need to call him\Nwith that message.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:21:00.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.75,0:21:31.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, you've reached\Nthe Goddess Help Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:32.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry, wrong number...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:33.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will take your request at your room.{\i0}\NOh, I'm sorry, wrong number...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.65,0:21:36.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will take your request at your room.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.01,0:21:39.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:22:00.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.95,0:22:07.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, what is your heart's desire?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.59,0:22:12.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, goodness gracious...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.99,0:22:15.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to introduce myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.13,0:22:22.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Goddess Belldandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.04,0:22:24.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,G-Goddess?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.97,0:22:26.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:29.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have come here for the\Nexpress purpose of saving...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.34,0:22:32.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...people in need of help,\Nsuch as yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.81,0:22:36.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, your wish is my command!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.51,0:22:38.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anything you desire...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.22,0:22:47.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will this turn of events bring\NKeiichi happiness? Or misery?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:52.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A new path has opened up\Nin this young man's destiny...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.63,0:22:58.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether or not he decides to\Nfollow it, is entirely up to him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.35,0:23:13.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One day when I woke up...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.76,0:23:24.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A day like any other...\Nanother one just beginning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.46,0:23:33.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There you are, yawning...\Nyour face is still so sleepy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.94,0:23:40.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because each peaceful day\Nwe share is a miracle to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.61,0:23:47.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is where my heart\Nwill always return...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.22,0:23:50.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forever...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.08,0:23:56.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's only one thing I wish for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:24:02.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I chase after the same dream,\Nwherever it may go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.44,0:24:08.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The love I feel for you\Ngives me strength.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.44,0:24:14.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}May tomorrow be as joyful as today...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:19.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's my wish...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.96,0:24:34.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The goddess has descended on\Nthis sacred spot... a six-mat room.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.90,0:24:37.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy proclaimed to me\Nin a song-like voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.80,0:24:39.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have come to grant your wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.74,0:24:42.88,AMG next episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Ah! Those Who Believe\NShall Find Salvation!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.88,0:24:45.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really okay with this tiny room?
